      "name": "Pump pressure-rise curve validation across speed range",
      "description": "Experimental head-flow curves compared against CFD predictions at 3000, 4000, and 5000 RPM. Agreement within 12% across operating range. Validation result recorded without hasUncertaintyQuantification field populated."
    }
