    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels across all categories. Six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. The team determined that the overall evidence package, combined with the Monte Carlo UQ framework and the FDA generic pump validation dataset, provides sufficient basis to support the intended use decision for the VAD hemolysis prediction context of use.",
